r-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">nice and easy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yerihs\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8f3c9e64f68802a552e1eda65e7798c4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8f3c9e64f68802a552e1eda65e7798c4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yerihs\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yerihs</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 29, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It\'s simple to use, easy to understand and it works. The quickest fix I\'ve had in a good while!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use redirection plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/calderwood\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4819a873e47d06ca125fde937d8ca0cd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4819a873e47d06ca125fde937d8ca0cd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/calderwood\" class=\"reviewer-name\">calderwood</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Set it up in less than 30 seconds. Enter the old page, add the new custom link or if the new page is on the site, really easy, just select page/post from drop-down. Click done. So simple and easy to use, plus really effective. I think this is my new go-to redirection plugin. Does not have 404 error logging yet - but there is a tab that says coming soon.  That would make it 6 stars.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use and works great!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sidonieyang\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/afc0fc5601a9e065d43f2ff41eca8e20?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/afc0fc5601a9e065d43f2ff41eca8e20?s=3